{
  "stem": "1042.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We start to go on bikes, and then we start to race on bikes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maccabee, I joined-- I joined, since my childhood, when I was 15, 16 till 20, 21.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had to serve the Polish Army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in the Polish Army--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1934.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's-- you know, as a Jew, and I was-- and my health position was very good.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I had to go wherever they sent me, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was cavalry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I was, because I had my papers that I am a mechanic and a driver, so my chief, the chief, the Major of the [INAUDIBLE] where I was there, he took me right away.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had a car, an old one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I fixed a little bit the car.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was, as a driver, working with him, going whenever he asked for.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And even so far we were, you know, in good terms.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He likes me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And whenever he used to leave out of town, he gave me the car.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said, you just keep the car and you're the responsible one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the army was very, very hard, you know, in the Polish Army, and special for Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Matter of fact, that-- one of the Jews commit suicide.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, it was so hard because the anti-Semitism was also in the Army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But because my boss was a Colonel, this was the main on the all, you know-- in the all [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was the-- the only one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But being in one of the special was a Rotemeister.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was inside the one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But outside was the Colonel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And because it started that time already that I find out that I did a very smart move that I learned this profession.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That's why I was, you know, I would say one only.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "What I didn't feel so much, you know, this anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know, when my Colonel used to go out of town, so my Rotemeister, the inside chief, was with his wife and children, he was coming to me, begging me if it's possible I shall take him to the hospital with the children.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that's why I always, even being in the Army, I was a free man.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know, whenever I wanted to be at home, even dressed as a soldier, I used to come for, you know, lunch at home, and for the weekends I had free when the Colonel didn't need me.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And others, you know, had very, very hard work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was with horses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They used to go at night to work in the stables, you know, to clean up from the horses.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I didn't feel it, this, you know, because I was special.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I was really like a chosen one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "For then, that time, somebody, a mechanic, an auto mechanic and a driver, was really, you know, very few.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So that was for three years I was in the Army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the Army, I got out end of '36, beginning of '37. 1937 I finished.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went back home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I wanted to move to Israel, and I had all my papers prepared.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when they find out that I want to move to Palestine-- at that time, it wasn't Israel.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was Palestine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they called me after a year, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] or after two years, they called me back for exercise, again, to the Army.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What I was supposed to go after three years, but they didn't want to let me out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, it was because of anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They didn't want, as a Jew, I should go to-- to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Even they always used to say, Jews, they belong to Palestine, but if come the time somebody had the possibility to-- to go to Palestine, it was very hard.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they took me to the-- for the exercises, you know, maneuvers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was there for two months, again, as a driver.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I didn't feel-- remember this was out of town, far away, you know, till after [INAUDIBLE], all the Polish states who used to-- they used to go on the horses.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I used to go with my Colonel in the car, or a motorcycle with a bi-wagon.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then they let me free.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I finished, but they didn't let me go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they start to talk about a war is coming that Hitler started.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People used to run away from Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the-- my brothers and one of the sisters-- because in meantime, one sister left for Palestine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The brother, he called her out to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the sister with the children what was at home, and the bother, married with children, they was begging me, I shouldn't go.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I shouldn't leave them alone at home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I shall stay with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
